---
title: Chorizo Tortilla Stacks with Lime Crema and Sweet Pepper Salad
description: What's better than a quesadilla? A whole stack of quesadillas sliced into cheesy wedges of deliciousness! We snuck some extra veggies into the spiced chorizo filling.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/gateau-de-tortillas-au-chorizo-bbc71817.jpg
